\v 26 (25) 我​在​<a name="01902202600010;01902202600012" ll="SDBH:קָהָל:000000;SDBH:רַב:000001">大会</a>​中​<a name="01902202600006" ll="SDBH:תְּהִלָּה:000000">赞美</a>​你​的​话​是​从​你​而​来​，​我​要​在​<a name="01902202600020" ll="SDBH:יָרֵא:000000">敬畏</a>​耶和华​<a name="01902202600020" ll="SDBH:יָרֵא:000000">的</a>​人​面前​<a name="01902202600016" ll="SDBH:שׁלם:000004">还</a>​我​的​<a name="01902202600014" ll="SDBH:נֶדֶר:000000">愿</a>​。
    
\v 27 (26) 愿​<a name="01902202700004" ll="SDBH:עָנָו:000000">困苦</a>​的​人​<a name="01902202700002" ll="SDBH:אכל:000000">吃</a>​得​<a name="01902202700008" ll="SDBH:שׂבע:000000">饱足</a>​，​愿​<a name="01902202700014" ll="SDBH:דרשׁ:000003">寻求</a>​<a name="01902202700012" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">耶和华</a>​的​人​<a name="01902202700010" ll="SDBH:הלל:001000">赞美</a>​他​。​愿​你们​的​<a name="01902202700018" ll="SDBH:לֵבָב:000001">心</a>​<a name="01902202700022" ll="SDBH:עַד:001000">永远</a>​<a name="01902202700016" ll="SDBH:חיה:000006">活</a>​着​！
    
\v 28 (27) <a name="01902202800016" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000">地</a>​的​<a name="01902202800012;01902202800014" ll="SDBH:אֶפֶס:000002">四极</a>​都​要​<a name="01902202800002" ll="SDBH:זכר:000000">想念</a>​<a name="01902202800010" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">耶和华</a>​，​并且​<a name="01902202800006" ll="SDBH:שׁוב:000005">归顺</a>​他​，​<a name="01902202800030" ll="SDBH:גֹּוי:000000" il="jlm_soltemp_d01;jlm_soltemp_m06;jlm_soltemp_pillars_m01">列国</a>​的​<a name="01902202800026;01902202800028" ll="SDBH:מִשְׁפָּחָה:000000">万族</a>​都​要​在​你​<a name="01902202800024">面前</a>​<a name="01902202800020" ll="SDBH:חוה:001000" il="Prostrate_figures">敬拜</a>​。
    
\v 29 (28) 因为​<a name="01902202900010" ll="SDBH:מְלוּכָה:000000">国度</a>​属于​<a name="01902202900006" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">耶和华</a>​，​他​是​<a name="01902202900014" ll="SDBH:משׁל:001000">管理</a>​<a name="01902202900020" ll="SDBH:גֹּוי:000000">列国</a>​的​。
    
\v 30 (29) <a name="01902203000012" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000">地</a>​<a name="01902203000012" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000">上</a>​<a name="01902203000010" ll="SDBH:דָּשֵׁן:000001" tl="HOTTP2155">富足</a>​的​人​<a name="01902203000008" tl="HOTTP2155">都</a>​必​<a name="01902203000002" ll="SDBH:אכל:000000" tl="HOTTP2154">吃喝</a>​而​<a name="01902203000006" ll="SDBH:חוה:001000" il="Prostrate_figures" tl="HOTTP2154">敬拜</a>​，​<a name="01902203000020">凡</a>​<a name="01902203000022" ll="SDBH:ירד:000004">下</a>​到​<a name="01902203000024" ll="SDBH:עָפָר:000000">尘土</a>​中​不​能​<a name="01902203000032" ll="SDBH:חיה:000001" tl="HOTTP2156">存活</a>​自己​<a name="01902203000028" ll="SDBH:נֶפֶשׁ:000001" tl="HOTTP2156">性命</a>​的​人​，​都​要​在​他​<a name="01902203000016">面前</a>​<a name="01902203000018" ll="SDBH:כרע:000000" il="Kneeling_Saint">下拜</a>​；
    
\v 31 (30) 必​有​<a name="01902203100002" ll="SDBH:זֶרַע:000004" il="Children_of_Kabul,_Afghanistan" tl="HOTTP2157">后裔</a>​<a name="01902203100004" ll="SDBH:עבד:000002">事奉</a>​他​，​<a name="01902203100010" ll="SDBH:אֲדֹנָי:000000">主</a>​所​做​的​事​必​<a name="01902203100006" ll="SDBH:ספר:000006">传给</a>​<a name="01902203100016" ll="SDBH:דֹּור:001000">后代</a>​。
    
\v 32 (31) 他们​必​<a name="01902203200002">来</a>​<a name="01902203200006" ll="SDBH:נגד:000000">传</a>​他​的​<a name="01902203200008" ll="SDBH:צְדָקָה:000001">公义</a>​给​尚未​<a name="01902203200014" ll="SDBH:ילד:000000" il="Baby_boy_after_birth;Birth;Children_of_Kabul,_Afghanistan">出生</a>​的​<a name="01902203200012" ll="SDBH:עַם:000000">子民</a>​，​这​是​他​的​<a name="01902203200018">作为</a>​。
\c 23
\v 1 <a name="01902300100008" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">耶和华</a>​是​我​的​<a name="01902300100010" ll="SDBH:רעה:000003" il="BK00005;BK00010;HK00009;LB00001;LB00013;NBGpb20140401b;Realia:1.2.1;Shepherd">牧者</a>​，​我​必​不致​<a name="01902300100014" ll="SDBH:חסר:000001">缺乏</a>​。
    
\v 2 他​使​我​<a name="01902300200008" ll="SDBH:רבץ:000001">躺卧</a>​在​<a name="01902300200004;01902300200006" ll="SDBH:דֶּשֶׁא:000000;SDBH:נָוָה:000001">青草地</a>​上​，​<a name="01902300200016" ll="SDBH:נהל:000001">领</a>​我​在​<a name="01902300200014" ll="SDBH:מְנוּחָה:000001">可</a>​<a name="01902300200014" ll="SDBH:מְנוּחָה:000001">安歇</a>​<a name="01902300200014" ll="SDBH:מְנוּחָה:000001">的</a>​<a name="01902300200012" ll="SDBH:מַיִם:000000" il="Water_drop_001">水边</a>​。
    
\v 3 他​使​我​的​<a name="01902300300002" ll="SDBH:נֶפֶשׁ:000001">灵魂</a>​<a name="01902300300004" ll="SDBH:שׁוב:000039">苏醒</a>​，​为​自己​的​<a name="01902300300016" ll="SDBH:שֵׁם:000002">名</a>​<a name="01902300300006" ll="SDBH:נחה:000000">引导</a>​我​走​<a name="01902300300010;01902300300012" ll="SDBH:מַעְגָּל:000001;SDBH:צֶדֶק:000001">义路</a>​。
    
\v 4 我​虽然​<a name="01902300400006" ll="SDBH:הלך:000001">行过</a>​<a name="01902300400012" ll="SDBH:צַלְמָוֶת:000000">死荫</a>​的​<a name="01902300400010">幽谷</a>​，​也​不​<a name="01902300400016" ll="SDBH:ירא:000000">怕</a>​<a name="01902300400018" ll="SDBH:רַע:000004">遭害</a>​，​因为​你​与​我​同在​；​你​的​<a name="01902300400026" ll="SDBH:שֵׁבֶט:000000">杖</a>​、​你​的​<a name="01902300400030" ll="SDBH:מִשְׁעֶנֶת:000000">竿</a>​，​都​<a name="01902300400034" ll="SDBH:נחם:000000">安慰</a>​我​。
    
\v 5 在​我​<a name="01902300500012" ll="SDBH:צרר:000009">敌人</a>​面前​，​你​<a name="01902300500006">为</a>​我​<a name="01902300500002" ll="SDBH:ערך:000001">摆设</a>​<a name="01902300500008" ll="SDBH:שֻׁלְחָן:000000" il="Realia:5.7b">筵席</a>​；​你​用​<a name="01902300500020" ll="SDBH:שֶׁמֶן:000000" il="Italian_olive_oil_2007;NBGbs20100214-0211;il_oil_press_d01">油</a>​<a name="01902300500014" ll="SDBH:דשׁן:000003" il="Anoint">膏</a>​了​我​的​<a name="01902300500022" ll="SDBH:רֹאשׁ:000000">头</a>​，​使​我​的​<a name="01902300500024" ll="SDBH:כֹּוס:000000" il="adr1306212845">福杯</a>​<a name="01902300500026" ll="SDBH:רְוָיָה:000000">满溢</a>​。
    
\v 6 我​<a name="01902300600012;01902300600014;01902300600016" ll="SDBH:חַיִּים:000000;SDBH:יֹום:000004">一生一世</a>​必​有​<a name="01902300600004" ll="SDBH:טֹוב:000002">恩惠</a>​<a name="01902300600008" ll="SDBH:חֶסֶד:000000">慈爱</a>​<a name="01902300600010" ll="SDBH:רדף:000002">随</a>​着​我​；​我​且​要​<a name="01902300600020" ll="SDBH:שׁוב:000055" tl="HOTTP2158">住</a>​在​<a name="01902300600026" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">耶和华</a>​的​<a name="01902300600024" ll="SDBH:בַּיִת:000000" il="HK00232;HK00245;LB00235;NBGbs20090430-1_87;NBGbs20110223-127;NBGlo20140606;NBGlo20140606b;NBGlo20140708c;NBGlo20140825;NBGmk20120826;NBGmk20120826a;NBGmk20140917;jlm_sol_complex_ann;jlm_soltemp_altar_m01;jlm_soltemp_d01;jlm_soltemp_m06;jlm_soltemp_pillars_m01">殿</a>​中​，​直到​<a name="01902300600030;01902300600032" ll="SDBH:אֹרֶךְ:000001;SDBH:יֹום:000004">永远</a>​。
\c 24
\v 1 <a name="01902400100014" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000">地</a>​和​其中​<a name="01902400100018" ll="SDBH:מְלֹא:000000">所</a>​<a name="01902400100018" ll="SDBH:מְלֹא:000000">充满</a>​<a name="01902400100018" ll="SDBH:מְלֹא:000000">的</a>​，​<a name="01902400100020" ll="SDBH:תֵּבֵל:000000">世界</a>​和​<a name="01902400100024" tl="HOTTP2159">住</a>​在​其中​的​，​都​属​<a name="01902400100010" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">耶和华</a>​。
    
\v 2 他​把​地​<a name="01902400200010" ll="SDBH:יסד:000000">建立</a>​在​<a name="01902400200008" ll="SDBH:יָם:000000" il="Rough_seas">海</a>​上​，​<a name="01902400200018" ll="SDBH:כון:000001">安定</a>​在​<a name="01902400200016" ll="SDBH:נָהָר:000002">江河</a>​之上​。
    
\v 3 谁​能​<a name="01902400300004" ll="SDBH:עלה:000004">登</a>​<a name="01902400300010" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">耶和华</a>​的​<a name="01902400300008" ll="SDBH:הַר:000000">山</a>​？​谁​能​<a name="01902400300016">站</a>​在​他​的​<a name="01902400300020;01902400300022" ll="SDBH:מָקֹום:000000;SDBH:קֹדֶשׁ:000001">圣所</a>​？
    
\v 4 就是​<a name="01902400400004" ll="SDBH:כַּף:000001">手</a>​<a name="01902400400002" ll="SDBH:נָקִי:000000">洁</a>​<a name="01902400400010" ll="SDBH:לֵבָב:000001">心</a>​<a name="01902400400008" ll="SDBH:בַּר:001003">清</a>​，​<a name="01902400400024" ll="SDBH:נֶפֶשׁ:000001">意念</a>​不​向​<a name="01902400400022" ll="SDBH:שָׁוְא:000000">虚妄</a>​，​<a name="01902400400030" ll="SDBH:שׁבע:000000" il="Oath_Jacob_Esau">起誓</a>​不​怀​<a name="01902400400034" ll="SDBH:מִרְמָה:000000">诡诈</a>​的​人​。
    
\v 5 他​必​<a name="01902400500002;01902400500004" ll="SDBH:בְּרָכָה:000000;SDBH:נשׂא:000015">蒙</a>​<a name="01902400500010" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">耶和华</a>​<a name="01902400500002;01902400500004" ll="SDBH:בְּרָכָה:000000;SDBH:נשׂא:000015">赐福</a>​，​又​蒙​<a name="01902400500020" ll="SDBH:יֵשַׁע:000000">救</a>​他​的​<a name="01902400500018" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000002">上帝</a>​使​他​成​<a name="01902400500014" ll="SDBH:צְדָקָה:000001">义</a>​。
    
\v 6 这​是​<a name="01902400600008" ll="SDBH:דרשׁ:000003">寻求</a>​耶和华​的​<a name="01902400600004" ll="SDBH:דֹּור:001001">族类</a>​，​是​<a name="01902400600010" ll="SDBH:בקשׁ:000001">寻求</a>​你​<a name="01902400600012" ll="SDBH:פָּנֶה:000000" tl="HOTTP2160">面</a>​的​<a name="01902400600014" ll="SDBH:יַעֲקֹב:000000" tl="HOTTP2160">雅各</a>​。​（​细拉​）
    
