\v 7 (6) 当​他​<a name="01904100700006">来</a>​<a name="01904100700010" ll="SDBH:ראה:000000">看</a>​我​的​时候​，​<a name="01904100700014" ll="SDBH:דבר:001000">说</a>​的​是​<a name="01904100700012" ll="SDBH:שָׁוְא:000000">假话</a>​；​他​<a name="01904100700016" ll="SDBH:לֵב:000001">心</a>​<a name="01904100700018" ll="SDBH:קבץ:000003">存</a>​<a name="01904100700020" ll="SDBH:אָוֶן:000000">奸恶</a>​，​<a name="01904100700024" ll="SDBH:יצא:000000">走</a>​到​<a name="01904100700030" ll="SDBH:חוּץ:000000" il="HK00169;Realia:3.13.2;tb052001215">外边</a>​才​<a name="01904100700032" ll="SDBH:דבר:001000">说</a>​出来​。
    
