\v 2 (1) <a name="01904200200022" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000002">上帝</a>​啊​，​我​的​<a name="01904200200016" ll="SDBH:נֶפֶשׁ:000001">心</a>​<a name="01904200200018" ll="SDBH:ערג:000001">切慕</a>​你​，​如​<a name="01904200200004" ll="SDBH:אַיָּל:000000" il="Fauna:2.11a;Fauna:2.11b;HK00031;LB00034" tl="HOTTP2222">鹿</a>​<a name="01904200200006" ll="SDBH:ערג:000000">切慕</a>​<a name="01904200200010;01904200200012" ll="SDBH:אָפִיק:000000;SDBH:מַיִם:000000" il="Water_drop_001">溪水</a>​。
    
