\v 7 (6) 你们​要​向​<a name="01904700700004" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000002" tl="HOTTP2240">上帝</a>​<a name="01904700700002" ll="SDBH:זמר:000000" il="HK00188">歌颂</a>​，​<a name="01904700700006" ll="SDBH:זמר:000000" il="HK00188">歌颂</a>​！​向​我们​的​<a name="01904700700012" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">王</a>​<a name="01904700700008" ll="SDBH:זמר:000000" il="HK00188">歌颂</a>​，​<a name="01904700700014" ll="SDBH:זמר:000000" il="HK00188">歌颂</a>​！
    
\v 8 (7) 因为​<a name="01904700800012" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000002">上帝</a>​是​<a name="01904700800006;01904700800010" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000">全地</a>​的​<a name="01904700800004" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">王</a>​，​你们​要​用​<a name="01904700800016" ll="SDBH:מַשְׂכִּיל:000000">圣诗</a>​<a name="01904700800014" ll="SDBH:זמר:000000" il="HK00188">歌颂</a>​！
    
\v 9 (8) <a name="01904700900004" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000002">上帝</a>​<a name="01904700900002" ll="SDBH:מלך:000000">作</a>​<a name="01904700900002" ll="SDBH:מלך:000000">王</a>​治理​<a name="01904700900008" ll="SDBH:גֹּוי:000000">列国</a>​，​<a name="01904700900010" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000002">上帝</a>​<a name="01904700900012">坐</a>​在​他​的​<a name="01904700900018" ll="SDBH:קֹדֶשׁ:000001">圣</a>​<a name="01904700900016" ll="SDBH:כִּסֵּא:000000" il="Ashur-nasir-pal_II_throne;Darius_In_Parse;Roman_throne;Throne_Greek;Throne_Toutankamon;adr1603194845;mb120901102">宝座</a>​上​。
    
\v 10 (9) <a name="01904701000004" ll="SDBH:עַם:000000">万民</a>​的​<a name="01904701000002" ll="SDBH:נָדִיב:000001">君王</a>​<a name="01904701000006" ll="SDBH:אסף:000000">聚集</a>​，​要​作​<a name="01904701000012" ll="SDBH:אַבְרָהָם:000000" il="adr1305165446" tl="HOTTP2241">亚伯拉罕</a>​的​<a name="01904701000010" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000001" tl="HOTTP2241">上帝</a>​的​<a name="01904701000008" tl="HOTTP2241">子民</a>​，​因为​<a name="01904701000022" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000">地</a>​<a name="01904701000022" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000">上</a>​的​<a name="01904701000020" ll="SDBH:מָגֵן:000000" il="NBGmk20131008">盾牌</a>​是​属​<a name="01904701000018" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000002">上帝</a>​的​，​他​<a name="01904701000024;01904701000026" ll="SDBH:מְאֹד:000001;SDBH:עלה:000016">为</a>​<a name="01904701000024;01904701000026" ll="SDBH:מְאֹד:000001;SDBH:עלה:000016">至高</a>​！
