\v 9 (8) 我们​在​<a name="01904800900018" ll="SDBH:צָבָא:000006">万军</a>​之​<a name="01904800900016" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">耶和华</a>​的​<a name="01904800900014" ll="SDBH:עִיר:000000">城</a>​里​，​就是​我们​<a name="01904800900024" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000001">上帝</a>​的​<a name="01904800900022" ll="SDBH:עִיר:000000">城</a>​里​，​所​<a name="01904800900010" ll="SDBH:ראה:000000">看见</a>​的​正如​我们​所​<a name="01904800900006">听见</a>​的​。​<a name="01904800900026" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000002">上帝</a>​必​<a name="01904800900028" ll="SDBH:כון:000025">坚立</a>​这​城​，​直到​<a name="01904800900032" ll="SDBH:עֹולָם:000000">永远</a>​。​（​细拉​）
    
\v 10 (9) <a name="01904801000004" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000002">上帝</a>​啊​，​我们​在​你​的​<a name="01904801000012" ll="SDBH:הֵיכָל:000000">殿</a>​<a name="01904801000010">中</a><a name="01904801000002" ll="SDBH:דמה:001004">想念</a>​你​的​<a name="01904801000006" ll="SDBH:חֶסֶד:000000">慈爱</a>​。
    
\v 11 (10) <a name="01904801100006" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000002">上帝</a>​啊​，​你​受​的​<a name="01904801100010" ll="SDBH:תְּהִלָּה:000000">赞美</a>​正​与​你​的​<a name="01904801100004" ll="SDBH:שֵׁם:000002">名</a>​相称​，​直到​<a name="01904801100014;01904801100016" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000;SDBH:קָצוּ:000000">地极</a>​！​你​的​<a name="01904801100022" ll="SDBH:יָמִין:000000">右手</a>​<a name="01904801100020" ll="SDBH:מלא:000008">满</a>​了​<a name="01904801100018" ll="SDBH:צֶדֶק:000001">公义</a>​。
    
\v 12 (11) 因​你​的​<a name="01904801200016" ll="SDBH:מִשְׁפָּט:000001" il="Tel-dan-israelite-gate-im-tor">判断</a>​，​<a name="01904801200006" ll="SDBH:צִיֹּון:000000" il="tb060716478">锡安</a>​<a name="01904801200004" ll="SDBH:הַר:000000">山</a>​应当​<a name="01904801200002" ll="SDBH:שׂמח:000000">欢喜</a>​，​
    <a name="01904801200012" ll="SDBH:יְהוּדָה:000000">犹大</a>​的​<a name="01904801200010" ll="SDBH:בַּת:000001;SDBH:בַּת:000003">城镇</a>​应当​<a name="01904801200008" ll="SDBH:גיל:000000">快乐</a>​。
    
\v 13 (12) 你们​当​<a name="01904801300002">周游</a>​<a name="01904801300004" ll="SDBH:צִיֹּון:000000" il="tb060716478">锡安</a>​，​<a name="01904801300008" ll="SDBH:נקף:001002">四围</a>​<a name="01904801300008" ll="SDBH:נקף:001002">环绕</a>​，​<a name="01904801300010" ll="SDBH:ספר:000000">数点</a>​<a name="01904801300012" ll="SDBH:מִגְדָּל:000000" il="NBGpb20140401a">城楼</a>​，
    
\v 14 (13) <a name="01904801400002;01904801400004" ll="SDBH:לֵב:000001;SDBH:שׁית:000011">细看</a>​它​的​<a name="01904801400008" ll="SDBH:חֵיל:000000">城郭</a>​，​<a name="01904801400010" ll="SDBH:פסג:000000">察看</a>​它​的​<a name="01904801400012" ll="SDBH:אַרְמֹון:000000">宫殿</a>​，​为​要​<a name="01904801400016" ll="SDBH:ספר:000006">传扬</a>​给​<a name="01904801400020;01904801400022" ll="SDBH:אַחֲרֹון:000001;SDBH:דֹּור:001000">后代</a>​。
    
\v 15 (14) 因为​这​<a name="01904801500006" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000002">上帝</a>​<a name="01904801500010;01904801500014" ll="SDBH:עַד:001000;SDBH:עֹולָם:000000">永永远远</a>​为​我们​的​<a name="01904801500008" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000001">上帝</a>​，​他​必​作​我们​<a name="01904801500018">引路</a>​的​，​直到​<a name="01904801500022" ll="SDBH:מות:000000" tl="HOTTP2243">死</a>​时​。
\c 49
\v 4 (3) 我​<a name="01904900400002" ll="SDBH:פֶּה:000000">口</a>​要​<a name="01904900400004" ll="SDBH:דבר:001000">说</a>​<a name="01904900400006" ll="SDBH:חָכְמָה:000000">智慧</a>​的​言语​，​我​<a name="01904900400012" ll="SDBH:לֵב:000001">心</a>​<a name="01904900400010" ll="SDBH:הָגוּת:000000">思想</a>​<a name="01904900400014" ll="SDBH:תְּבוּנָה:000000">通达</a>​的​道理​。
    
\v 5 (4) 我​要​<a name="01904900500002;01904900500008" ll="SDBH:אֹזֶן:000000;SDBH:נטה:000003">侧耳</a>​<a name="01904900500002;01904900500008" ll="SDBH:אֹזֶן:000000;SDBH:נטה:000003">听</a>​<a name="01904900500006" ll="SDBH:מָשָׁל:000000">比喻</a>​，​用​<a name="01904900500014" ll="SDBH:כִּנֹּור:000000" il="BK00175;BK00176;Exile_Lachish;HK00188;NBGmk20131114;adr1306213109;tb072705188">琴</a>​<a name="01904900500010" ll="SDBH:פתח:000009">解</a>​<a name="01904900500016" ll="SDBH:חִידָה:000000">谜语</a>​。
    
\v 6 (5) 在​<a name="01904900600010" ll="SDBH:רַע:000004">患难</a>​的​<a name="01904900600008" ll="SDBH:יֹום:000003">日子</a>​，​追逼​我​的​人​的​<a name="01904900600012" ll="SDBH:עָוֹן:000000">奸恶</a>​<a name="01904900600016">环绕</a>​我​，​我​何必​<a name="01904900600004" ll="SDBH:ירא:000000">惧怕</a>​？
    
\v 7 (6) 他们​那些​<a name="01904900700004" ll="SDBH:בטח:000001">倚靠</a>​<a name="01904900700008" ll="SDBH:חַיִל:000001">财货</a>​，​<a name="01904900700018" ll="SDBH:הלל:001002">自夸</a>​<a name="01904900700016" ll="SDBH:עֹשֶׁר:000000">钱财</a>​<a name="01904900700014" ll="SDBH:רֹב:000001">多</a>​的​人​，
    
\v 8 (7) <a name="01904900800010" tl="HOTTP2244">没有</a>​<a name="01904900800010" tl="HOTTP2244">一</a>​<a name="01904900800010" tl="HOTTP2244">个</a>​能​<a name="01904900800008" ll="SDBH:פדה:000000" tl="HOTTP2244">赎</a>​自己​的​<a name="01904900800002" ll="SDBH:אָח:000007" tl="HOTTP2244">弟兄</a>​，​能​将​<a name="01904900800020" ll="SDBH:כֹּפֶר:000001">赎价</a>​<a name="01904900800014">给</a>​<a name="01904900800018" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000002">上帝</a>​，
    
\v 11 (10) 他​要​<a name="01904901100004" ll="SDBH:ראה:000000" tl="HOTTP2245">见</a>​<a name="01904901100006" ll="SDBH:חָכָם, קסם:000000">智慧人</a>​<a name="01904901100008" ll="SDBH:מות:000000">死</a>​，​<a name="01904901100012" ll="SDBH:כְּסִיל:000000">愚昧人</a>​和​<a name="01904901100016" ll="SDBH:בַּעַר:000000">畜牲</a>​<a name="01904901100016" ll="SDBH:בַּעַר:000000">一般</a>​<a name="01904901100016" ll="SDBH:בַּעַר:000000">的</a>​人​<a name="01904901100010">一同</a>​<a name="01904901100018" ll="SDBH:אבד:000004">灭亡</a>​，​把​他们​的​<a name="01904901100028" ll="SDBH:חַיִל:000001">财货</a>​<a name="01904901100022" ll="SDBH:עזב:000000">留给</a>​<a name="01904901100026" ll="SDBH:אַחֵר:000000">别人</a>​。
    
\v 12 (11) 他们​虽​以​自己​的​<a name="01904901200024" ll="SDBH:שֵׁם:000000">名</a>​<a name="01904901200020" ll="SDBH:קרא:000007">叫</a>​自己​的​<a name="01904901200028" ll="SDBH:אֲדָמָה:000000" il="Soil" tl="HOTTP2247">地</a>​，​坟墓​却​作​他们​<a name="01904901200008" ll="SDBH:עֹולָם:000000">永远</a>​的​<a name="01904901200004" ll="SDBH:בַּיִת:000000" il="HK00232;LB00235;NBGbs20090430-1_87;NBGbs20110223-127;NBGmk20120826;NBGmk20120826a;NBGmk20140917">家</a>​，​作​他们​<a name="01904901200014;01904901200018" ll="SDBH:דֹּור:001000">世世代代</a>​的​<a name="01904901200010" ll="SDBH:מִשְׁכָּן:000000">居所</a>​。
    
\v 13 (12) <a name="01904901300004" ll="SDBH:אָדָם:000000">人</a>​居​<a name="01904901300008" ll="SDBH:יְקָר:000000" tl="HOTTP2248">尊贵</a>​中​<a name="01904901300010" ll="SDBH:בַּל:000000" tl="HOTTP2249">不</a>​能​<a name="01904901300012" ll="SDBH:לין:000001" tl="HOTTP2249">长久</a>​，​<a name="01904901300014" ll="SDBH:משׁל:000000">如同</a>​<a name="01904901300022" ll="SDBH:דמה:000001">死亡</a>​的​<a name="01904901300020" ll="SDBH:בְּהֵמָה:000000">畜类</a>​一样​。
    
\v 14 (13) 他们​所​行​之​<a name="01904901400004" ll="SDBH:דֶּרֶךְ:000007">道</a>​本​为​自己​的​<a name="01904901400006" ll="SDBH:כֶּסֶל:002000">愚昧</a>​，​后来​的​人​却​还​<a name="01904901400018" ll="SDBH:רצה:000000">佩服</a>​他们​的​<a name="01904901400016" ll="SDBH:פֶּה:000001">话语</a>​。​（​细拉​）
    
\v 15 (14) 他们​如同​<a name="01904901500006" ll="SDBH:צֹאן:000000" il="LB00012;LB00015;LB00017;NBGbs20120208-08;NBGbs20120710-139;NBGpb20140401b;Realia:1.2.1;tb111706002">羊群</a>​<a name="01904901500012" ll="SDBH:שׁית:000001">注定</a>​要​下​<a name="01904901500010" ll="SDBH:שְׁאֹול:000000">阴间</a>​，​<a name="01904901500014" ll="SDBH:מָוֶת:000002">死亡</a>​必​<a name="01904901500016" ll="SDBH:רעה:000003" il="BK00005;BK00010;HK00009;LB00001;LB00013;NBGpb20140401b;Realia:1.2.1;Shepherd">作</a>​他们​的​<a name="01904901500016" ll="SDBH:רעה:000003" il="BK00005;BK00010;HK00009;LB00001;LB00013;NBGpb20140401b;Realia:1.2.1;Shepherd">牧者</a>​；​到​了​<a name="01904901500030" ll="SDBH:בֹּקֶר:000000" tl="HOTTP2251">早晨</a>​，​<a name="01904901500024" ll="SDBH:יָשָׁר:000004" tl="HOTTP2251">正直人</a>​必​<a name="01904901500020" ll="SDBH:רדה:000000" tl="HOTTP2251">管辖</a>​他们​。​他们​的​<a name="01904901500034" ll="SDBH:צוּר:001000">形像</a>​必​被​<a name="01904901500042" ll="SDBH:בלה:000002">阴间</a>​所​<a name="01904901500040">灭</a>​，​无处​可​<a name="01904901500046" tl="HOTTP2252">容身</a>​。
    
\v 16 (15) <a name="01904901600002" ll="SDBH:אַךְ:000004">然而</a>​<a name="01904901600004" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000002">上帝</a>​必​<a name="01904901600006" ll="SDBH:פדה:000002">救赎</a>​我​的​<a name="01904901600008" ll="SDBH:נֶפֶשׁ:000001">命</a>​脱离​<a name="01904901600014" ll="SDBH:שְׁאֹול:000000">阴间</a>​的​<a name="01904901600012">掌控</a>​，​因​他​必​<a name="01904901600018" ll="SDBH:לקח:000000">收纳</a>​我​。​（​细拉​）
    
\v 17 (16) 见​<a name="01904901700010">人</a>​<a name="01904901700008" ll="SDBH:עשׁר:000000">发财</a>​、​<a name="01904901700018" ll="SDBH:בַּיִת:000003">家室</a>​<a name="01904901700014">日益</a>​<a name="01904901700016" ll="SDBH:כָּבֹוד:000001">显赫</a>​的​时候​，​你​<a name="01904901700002" ll="SDBH:אַל:000000">不要</a>​<a name="01904901700004" ll="SDBH:ירא:000000">惧怕</a>​；
    
\v 18 (17) 因为​他​<a name="01904901800008" ll="SDBH:מָוֶת:000000">死</a>​的​时候​<a name="01904901800014">什么</a>​也​不​能​<a name="01904901800010" ll="SDBH:לקח:000000">带去</a>​，​他​的​<a name="01904901800022" ll="SDBH:כָּבֹוד:000001">荣耀</a>​不​能​随​他​<a name="01904901800018" ll="SDBH:ירד:000004">下去</a>​。
    
\v 19 (18) <a name="01904901900004" ll="SDBH:נֶפֶשׁ:000001">他</a>​<a name="01904901900008" ll="SDBH:חַיִּים:000000">活</a>​<a name="01904901900008" ll="SDBH:חַיִּים:000000">着</a>​的​时候​，​虽然​自夸​为​<a name="01904901900010" ll="SDBH:ברך:001001">有</a>​<a name="01904901900010" ll="SDBH:ברך:001001">福</a>—你​若​自己​<a name="01904901900018" ll="SDBH:יטב:000011">行</a>​<a name="01904901900018" ll="SDBH:יטב:000011">得</a>​<a name="01904901900018" ll="SDBH:יטב:000011">好</a>​，​人​必​<a name="01904901900014" ll="SDBH:ידה:000002">夸奖</a>​你​—
    
\v 20 (19) 他​仍​必​与​<a name="01904902000006" ll="SDBH:דֹּור:001001">历代</a>​的​<a name="01904902000008" ll="SDBH:אָב:000001">祖宗</a>​一样​同​<a name="01904902000002">归</a>​死亡​，​<a name="01904902000012" ll="SDBH:נֵצַח:000000">永不</a>​<a name="01904902000016" ll="SDBH:ראה:000004">见</a>​<a name="01904902000018" ll="SDBH:אֹור:000000">光</a>​。
    
\v 21 (20) <a name="01904902100002" ll="SDBH:אָדָם:000000">人</a>​在​<a name="01904902100006" ll="SDBH:יְקָר:000000" tl="HOTTP2253">尊贵</a>​中​而​不​<a name="01904902100012" ll="SDBH:בין:000001" tl="HOTTP2254">醒悟</a>​，​就​<a name="01904902100014" ll="SDBH:משׁל:000000">如</a>​<a name="01904902100022" ll="SDBH:דמה:000001">死亡</a>​的​<a name="01904902100020" ll="SDBH:בְּהֵמָה:000000">畜类</a>​一样​。
\c 50
\v 1 <a name="01905000100008" ll="SDBH:אֵל:000001">大能者</a>​<a name="01905000100010" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000002">上帝</a>​—​<a name="01905000100012" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">耶和华</a>​已经​<a name="01905000100014" ll="SDBH:דבר:001000">发言</a>​<a name="01905000100018" ll="SDBH:קרא:000003">呼召</a>​<a name="01905000100020" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000">天下</a>​，​从​<a name="01905000100024;01905000100026" ll="SDBH:מִזְרָח:000001;SDBH:שֶׁמֶשׁ:000000" il="Sun;Sun_pillar;Sunrise;Sunset;Sunset_on_mountain">日出</a>​<a name="01905000100024;01905000100026" ll="SDBH:מִזְרָח:000001;SDBH:שֶׁמֶשׁ:000000" il="Sun;Sun_pillar;Sunrise;Sunset;Sunset_on_mountain">之</a>​<a name="01905000100024;01905000100026" ll="SDBH:מִזְרָח:000001;SDBH:שֶׁמֶשׁ:000000" il="Sun;Sun_pillar;Sunrise;Sunset;Sunset_on_mountain">地</a>​到​<a name="01905000100030" ll="SDBH:מָבֹוא:000002">日落</a>​<a name="01905000100030" ll="SDBH:מָבֹוא:000002">之</a>​<a name="01905000100030" ll="SDBH:מָבֹוא:000002">处</a>​。
    
\v 2 从​<a name="01905000200006" ll="SDBH:מִכְלָל:000000">全然</a>​<a name="01905000200008" ll="SDBH:יֳפִי:000000">美丽</a>​的​<a name="01905000200004" ll="SDBH:צִיֹּון:000000" il="tb060716478">锡安</a>​中​，​<a name="01905000200010" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000002">上帝</a>​已经​<a name="01905000200012" ll="SDBH:יפע:000000;SDBH:יפע:000002">发光</a>​了​。
    
\v 3 我们​的​<a name="01905000300004" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000001">上帝</a>​要​<a name="01905000300002">来</a>​，​<a name="01905000300008" ll="SDBH:אַל:000000">绝不</a>​<a name="01905000300010" ll="SDBH:חרשׁ:001001">闭口</a>​；​有​<a name="01905000300012" ll="SDBH:אֵשׁ:000000" il="Fire02">烈火</a>​在​他​<a name="01905000300016">面前</a>​<a name="01905000300018" ll="SDBH:אכל:000002">吞灭</a>​，​有​<a name="01905000300024;01905000300026" ll="SDBH:מְאֹד:000001;SDBH:שׂער:001000">暴风</a>​在​他​<a name="01905000300022" ll="SDBH:סָבִיב:000000">四围</a>​<a name="01905000300024;01905000300026" ll="SDBH:מְאֹד:000001;SDBH:שׂער:001000">刮起</a>​。
    
\v 4 他​<a name="01905000400002" ll="SDBH:קרא:000000">呼召</a>​<a name="01905000400008;01905000400012" ll="SDBH:שָׁמַיִם:000001">上天</a>​<a name="01905000400020" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000">下地</a>​，​为​要​<a name="01905000400024" ll="SDBH:דין:000000">审判</a>​他​的​<a name="01905000400026" ll="SDBH:עַם:000000">子民</a>​：
    
\v 5 “​<a name="01905000500002" ll="SDBH:אסף:000001">召集</a>​我​的​<a name="01905000500006" ll="SDBH:חָסִיד:000000">圣民</a>​，​就是​那些​用​<a name="01905000500014" ll="SDBH:זֶבַח:000000">祭物</a>​与​我​<a name="01905000500008;01905000500010" ll="SDBH:בְּרִית:000000;SDBH:כרת:000001">立约</a>​的​人​，​到​我​这里​来​。​”
    
\v 6 <a name="01905000600006" ll="SDBH:שָׁמַיִם:000000">诸天</a>​必​<a name="01905000600004" ll="SDBH:נגד:000000">表明</a>​他​的​<a name="01905000600008" ll="SDBH:צֶדֶק:000001">公义</a>​，​因为​<a name="01905000600012" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000002">上帝</a>​是​<a name="01905000600014" ll="SDBH:שׁפט:000006" il="Tel-dan-israelite-gate-im-tor">施行</a>​<a name="01905000600014" ll="SDBH:שׁפט:000006" il="Tel-dan-israelite-gate-im-tor">审判</a>​的​。​（​细拉​）
    
\v 7 “​<a name="01905000700002">听</a>​啊​，​我​的​<a name="01905000700004" ll="SDBH:עַם:000000">子民</a>​，​我​要​<a name="01905000700008" ll="SDBH:דבר:001000">说话</a>​！​
