\v 22 我​的​<a name="01907102200016" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000001">上帝</a>​啊​，​我​要​<a name="01907102200010;01907102200012" ll="SDBH:כְּלִי:000000;SDBH:נֵבֶל:001000" il="BK00175;BK00176;Exile_Lachish;NBGmk20131114;adr1306213109;tb072705188">鼓瑟</a>​<a name="01907102200006" ll="SDBH:ידה:000002">称谢</a>​你​，​称谢​你​的​<a name="01907102200014" ll="SDBH:אֱמֶת:000000">信实</a>​！​
    <a name="01907102200028" ll="SDBH:יִשְׂרָאֵל:000000">以色列</a>​的​<a name="01907102200026" ll="SDBH:קָדֹושׁ:000000">圣者</a>​啊​，​我​要​<a name="01907102200024" ll="SDBH:כִּנֹּור:000000" il="BK00175;BK00176;Exile_Lachish;HK00188;NBGmk20131114;adr1306213109;tb072705188">弹琴</a>​<a name="01907102200018" ll="SDBH:זמר:000000" il="HK00188">歌颂</a>​你​！
    
