\v 12 (11) 我​要​<a name="01907701200004" ll="SDBH:זכר:000000">记念</a>​<a name="01907701200008" ll="SDBH:יָהּ:000000" tl="HOTTP2412">耶和华</a>​<a name="01907701200006" ll="SDBH:מַעֲלָל:000000" tl="HOTTP2412">所</a>​<a name="01907701200006" ll="SDBH:מַעֲלָל:000000" tl="HOTTP2412">做</a>​<a name="01907701200006" ll="SDBH:מַעֲלָל:000000" tl="HOTTP2412">的</a>​，​要​<a name="01907701200012" ll="SDBH:זכר:000000">记念</a>​你​<a name="01907701200016" ll="SDBH:קֶדֶם:000002">古时</a>​的​<a name="01907701200018" ll="SDBH:פֶּלֶא:000000">奇事</a>​；
    
\v 13 (12) 我​要​<a name="01907701300004" ll="SDBH:הגה:000001">思想</a>​你​<a name="01907701300010" ll="SDBH:פֹּעַל:000000">所</a>​<a name="01907701300010" ll="SDBH:פֹּעַל:000000">做</a>​<a name="01907701300010" ll="SDBH:פֹּעַל:000000">的</a>​，​<a name="01907701300018" ll="SDBH:שׂיח:000001">默念</a>​你​的​<a name="01907701300016" ll="SDBH:עֲלִילָה:000000">作为</a>​。
    
\v 14 (13) <a name="01907701400002" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000002">上帝</a>​啊​，​你​的​<a name="01907701400010" ll="SDBH:דֶּרֶךְ:000007">道</a>​是​<a name="01907701400008" ll="SDBH:קֹדֶשׁ:000001">神圣</a>​<a name="01907701400008" ll="SDBH:קֹדֶשׁ:000001">的</a>​；​有​何​<a name="01907701400014" ll="SDBH:אֵל:000001">神明</a>​<a name="01907701400016" ll="SDBH:גָּדֹול:000002">大</a>​如​<a name="01907701400020" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000002">上帝</a>​呢​？
    
\v 15 (14) 你​是​<a name="01907701500008">行</a>​<a name="01907701500010" ll="SDBH:פֶּלֶא:000000">奇事</a>​的​<a name="01907701500006" ll="SDBH:אֵל:000001">上帝</a>​，​你​曾​在​<a name="01907701500018" ll="SDBH:עַם:000000">万民</a>​中​<a name="01907701500012">彰显</a>​<a name="01907701500020" ll="SDBH:עֹז:000002">能力</a>​。
    
\v 16 (15) 你​曾​用​<a name="01907701600006" ll="SDBH:זְרֹועַ:000000">膀臂</a>​<a name="01907701600002" ll="SDBH:גאל:000003">赎</a>​了​你​的​<a name="01907701600008" ll="SDBH:עַם:000000">子民</a>​，​就是​<a name="01907701600012" ll="SDBH:יַעֲקֹב:000000">雅各</a>​和​<a name="01907701600016" ll="SDBH:יֹוסֵף:000000">约瑟</a>​的​<a name="01907701600010" ll="SDBH:בֵּן:000000">子孙</a>​。​（​细拉​）
    
\v 17 (16) <a name="01907701700006" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000002">上帝</a>​啊​，​众​<a name="01907701700004" ll="SDBH:מַיִם:000000" il="Water_drop_001">水</a>​<a name="01907701700002" ll="SDBH:ראה:000000">见</a>​你​，​众​<a name="01907701700010" ll="SDBH:מַיִם:000000" il="Water_drop_001">水</a>​一​<a name="01907701700008" ll="SDBH:ראה:000000">见</a>​你​就​都​<a name="01907701700012" ll="SDBH:חיל:000002">惊惶</a>​，​<a name="01907701700018" ll="SDBH:תְּהֹום:000000">深渊</a>​也​都​<a name="01907701700016" ll="SDBH:רגז:000000">战抖</a>​。
    
\v 18 (17) <a name="01907701800006" ll="SDBH:עָב:000000" il="Altocumulus_cloud;White_cloud_111">密云</a>​<a name="01907701800002" ll="SDBH:זרם:000000">倒出</a>​<a name="01907701800004" ll="SDBH:מַיִם:000000" il="Water_drop_001">水</a>​来​，​<a name="01907701800012" ll="SDBH:שַׁחַק:000001">天空</a>​<a name="01907701800010">发出</a>​<a name="01907701800008">响声</a>​，​你​的​<a name="01907701800016" ll="SDBH:חֵץ:000001" il="Realia:2.14.1a;Realia:2.14.3;adr1005306124;adr1603194668">箭</a>​也​<a name="01907701800018" ll="SDBH:הלך:000000">飞行</a>​四方​。
    
\v 19 (18) 你​的​<a name="01907701900002;01907701900004" ll="SDBH:רַעַם:000000">雷声</a>​在​<a name="01907701900010" ll="SDBH:גַּלְגַּל:000000" il="Realia:8.2b">旋风</a>​之中​，​<a name="01907701900014" ll="SDBH:בָּרָק:000000" il="Lightning_14.07.2009_20-42-33">闪电</a>​<a name="01907701900012" ll="SDBH:אור:000001">照亮</a>​<a name="01907701900016" ll="SDBH:תֵּבֵל:000000">世界</a>​，​<a name="01907701900026" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000">大地</a>​<a name="01907701900018" ll="SDBH:רגז:000000">战抖</a>​<a name="01907701900022" ll="SDBH:רעשׁ:000000">震动</a>​。
    
\v 20 (19) 你​的​<a name="01907702000008" ll="SDBH:דֶּרֶךְ:000003">道</a>​在​<a name="01907702000006" ll="SDBH:יָם:000000" il="Rough_seas">海</a>​中​，​你​的​<a name="01907702000014">路</a>​在​<a name="01907702000018;01907702000020" ll="SDBH:מַיִם:000000" il="Water_drop_001">大水</a>​之中​，​你​的​<a name="01907702000024">脚踪</a>​无​人​<a name="01907702000028" ll="SDBH:לֹא:000000">知道</a>​。
    
\v 21 (20) 你​曾​藉​<a name="01907702100016" ll="SDBH:מֹשֶׁה:000000" il="TEN COMMANDMENTS">摩西</a>​和​<a name="01907702100020" ll="SDBH:אַהֲרֹן:000000">亚伦</a>​的​<a name="01907702100014">手</a>​<a name="01907702100002" ll="SDBH:נחה:000000">引导</a>​你​的​<a name="01907702100010" ll="SDBH:עַם:000000">百姓</a>​，​好像​领​<a name="01907702100008" ll="SDBH:צֹאן:000000" il="LB00012;LB00015;LB00017;NBGbs20120208-08;NBGbs20120710-139;NBGpb20140401b;Realia:1.2.1;tb111706002">羊群</a>​一般​。
\c 78
\v 1 我​的​<a name="01907800100010" ll="SDBH:עַם:000000">子民</a>​哪​，​要​<a name="01907800100008" ll="SDBH:אזן:000000">侧耳</a>​<a name="01907800100008" ll="SDBH:אזן:000000">听</a>​我​的​<a name="01907800100012" ll="SDBH:תֹּורָה:000000">训诲</a>​，​竖起​<a name="01907800100016" ll="SDBH:אֹזֶן:000000">耳朵</a>​听​我​<a name="01907800100022" ll="SDBH:פֶּה:000000">口</a>​中​的​<a name="01907800100020" ll="SDBH:אֵמֶר:000000">言语</a>​。
    
\v 2 我​要​<a name="01907800200002;01907800200008" ll="SDBH:פֶּה:000000;SDBH:פתח:000015">开口</a>​说​<a name="01907800200006" ll="SDBH:מָשָׁל:000000">比喻</a>​，​我​要​<a name="01907800200010" ll="SDBH:נבע:000002">解开</a>​<a name="01907800200016" ll="SDBH:קֶדֶם:000002">古时</a>​的​<a name="01907800200012" ll="SDBH:חִידָה:000000">谜语</a>​，
    
\v 3 是​我们​所​<a name="01907800300004">听见</a>​、​所​<a name="01907800300008">知道</a>​，​我们​的​<a name="01907800300012" ll="SDBH:אָב:000001">祖宗</a>​<a name="01907800300014" ll="SDBH:ספר:000006">告诉</a>​我们​的​。
    
\v 4 我们​不要​向​<a name="01907800400008" ll="SDBH:בֵּן:000000">子孙</a>​<a name="01907800400004" ll="SDBH:כחד:000001">隐瞒</a>​这些​事​，​而​要​将​<a name="01907800400020" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">耶和华</a>​的​<a name="01907800400018" ll="SDBH:תְּהִלָּה:000002">美德</a>​和​他​的​<a name="01907800400024" ll="SDBH:עֱזוּז:000000">能力</a>​，​并​他​所​<a name="01907800400032">行</a>​的​<a name="01907800400028" ll="SDBH:פלא:000000">奇事</a>​，​<a name="01907800400016" ll="SDBH:ספר:000006">述说</a>​给​<a name="01907800400012;01907800400014" ll="SDBH:אַחֲרֹון:000001;SDBH:דֹּור:001000">后代</a>​听​。
    
\v 5 他​在​<a name="01907800500010" ll="SDBH:יַעֲקֹב:000000">雅各</a>​中​<a name="01907800500004">立</a>​<a name="01907800500006" ll="SDBH:עֵדוּת:000000">法度</a>​，​在​<a name="01907800500020" ll="SDBH:יִשְׂרָאֵל:000000">以色列</a>​中​<a name="01907800500016" ll="SDBH:שׂים:000013">设</a>​<a name="01907800500014" ll="SDBH:תֹּורָה:000000">律法</a>​；​他​<a name="01907800500024" ll="SDBH:צוה:000000">吩咐</a>​我们​的​<a name="01907800500028" ll="SDBH:אָב:000001">祖宗</a>​要​<a name="01907800500032">传给</a>​<a name="01907800500036" ll="SDBH:בֵּן:000000">子孙</a>​，
    
\v 6 使​将​要​<a name="01907800600012" ll="SDBH:ילד:000000" il="Baby_boy_after_birth;Birth;Children_of_Kabul,_Afghanistan">生</a>​的​<a name="01907800600006;01907800600008" ll="SDBH:אַחֲרֹון:000001;SDBH:דֹּור:001000">后代</a>​<a name="01907800600010" ll="SDBH:בֵּן:000000">子孙</a>​可以​<a name="01907800600004">晓得</a>​。​他们​也​要​<a name="01907800600014">起来</a>​<a name="01907800600018" ll="SDBH:ספר:000006">告诉</a>​他们​的​<a name="01907800600022" ll="SDBH:בֵּן:000000">子孙</a>​，
    
\v 7 好​让​他们​<a name="01907800700004;01907800700010" ll="SDBH:כֶּסֶל:001000;SDBH:שׂים:000013">仰望</a>​<a name="01907800700008" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000002">上帝</a>​，​不​<a name="01907800700016" ll="SDBH:שׁכח:000000">忘记</a>​<a name="01907800700020" ll="SDBH:אֵל:000001">上帝</a>​的​<a name="01907800700018" ll="SDBH:מַעֲלָל:000000">作为</a>​，​惟​<a name="01907800700026" ll="SDBH:נצר:000001">遵守</a>​他​的​<a name="01907800700024" ll="SDBH:מִצְוָה:000000">命令</a>​；
    
\v 8 不要​像​他们​的​<a name="01907800800010" ll="SDBH:אָב:000001">祖宗</a>​，​是​<a name="01907800800014" ll="SDBH:סרר:000000">顽梗</a>​<a name="01907800800018" ll="SDBH:מרה:000000">悖逆</a>​、​<a name="01907800800026" ll="SDBH:לֵב:000001">心</a>​不​<a name="01907800800024" ll="SDBH:כון:000007">坚定</a>​，​向​<a name="01907800800036" ll="SDBH:אֵל:000001">上帝</a>​<a name="01907800800038" ll="SDBH:רוּחַ:000002">心</a>​不​<a name="01907800800032" ll="SDBH:אמן:000006">忠实</a>​之​<a name="01907800800012" ll="SDBH:דֹּור:001000">辈</a>​。
    
\v 9 
    <a name="01907800900004" ll="SDBH:אֶפְרַיִם:000000">以法莲</a>​<a name="01907800900002" ll="SDBH:בֵּן:000000">人</a>​<a name="01907800900006" ll="SDBH:נשׁק:001000">带</a>​着​<a name="01907800900006" ll="SDBH:נשׁק:001000">兵器</a>​，​拿​着​<a name="01907800900010" ll="SDBH:קֶשֶׁת:000000" il="Realia:2.14.1a;Realia:2.14.1b">弓</a>​，​<a name="01907800900018" ll="SDBH:קְרָב:000000">临阵</a>​之​<a name="01907800900016" ll="SDBH:יֹום:000003">日</a>​<a name="01907800900012" ll="SDBH:הפך:000000">转身</a>​<a name="01907800900012" ll="SDBH:הפך:000000">退后</a>​。
    
\v 10 他们​不​<a name="01907801000004" ll="SDBH:שׁמר:000003">遵守</a>​<a name="01907801000008" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000002">上帝</a>​的​<a name="01907801000006" ll="SDBH:בְּרִית:000000">约</a>​，​<a name="01907801000016" ll="SDBH:מאן:000000">不</a>​<a name="01907801000016" ll="SDBH:מאן:000000">肯</a>​照​他​的​<a name="01907801000014" ll="SDBH:תֹּורָה:000000">律法</a>​<a name="01907801000020" ll="SDBH:הלך:000004">行</a>​；
    
\v 11 又​<a name="01907801100004" ll="SDBH:שׁכח:000000">忘记</a>​他​的​<a name="01907801100006" ll="SDBH:עֲלִילָה:000000">作为</a>和​他​所​<a name="01907801100014" ll="SDBH:ראה:000003">彰显</a>​的​<a name="01907801100010" ll="SDBH:פלא:000000">奇事</a>​。
    
\v 12 他​在​<a name="01907801200014" ll="SDBH:מִצְרַיִם:000001" il="Egyptian_temple;Gizah_Pyramids;Goshen;NBGbs20120205-81;NBGbs20120205-82;NBGbs20120207-20;NBGbs20140204-40;tb010705951">埃及</a>​<a name="01907801200012" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000">地</a>​，​在​<a name="01907801200018" ll="SDBH:צֹעַן:000000">琐安</a>​<a name="01907801200016" ll="SDBH:שָׂדֶה:000001">田</a>​，​在​他们​<a name="01907801200004" ll="SDBH:אָב:000001">祖宗</a>​眼前​<a name="01907801200006">施行</a>​<a name="01907801200008" ll="SDBH:פֶּלֶא:000000">奇事</a>​。
    
\v 13 他​把​<a name="01907801300004" ll="SDBH:יָם:000000" il="Rough_seas">海</a>​<a name="01907801300002" ll="SDBH:בקע:000001">分开</a>​，​使​他们​<a name="01907801300008" ll="SDBH:עבר:000001">过去</a>​，​又​叫​<a name="01907801300014" ll="SDBH:מַיִם:000000" il="Water_drop_001">水</a>​<a name="01907801300012" ll="SDBH:נצב:000001">立起</a>​如​<a name="01907801300018" ll="SDBH:נֵד:000000">垒</a>​。
    
\v 14 他​<a name="01907801400012" ll="SDBH:יֹומָם:000000">白日</a>​用​<a name="01907801400010" ll="SDBH:עָנָן:000000" il="Altocumulus_cloud;Pillar_of_cloud;White_cloud_111">云彩</a>​，​<a name="01907801400016;01907801400020" ll="SDBH:לַיְלָה:000000">终夜</a>​用​<a name="01907801400024;01907801400026" ll="SDBH:אֵשׁ:000000;SDBH:אֹור:000000" il="Fire02">火光</a>​<a name="01907801400004" ll="SDBH:נחה:000000">引导</a>​他们​。
    
\v 15 他​在​<a name="01907801500010" ll="SDBH:מִדְבָּר:000000" il="RS26447_ISR91T-418;Sinai-191;Sinai-220;Sinai-3;Sinai178;Sinai190;tb113006604">旷野</a>​使​<a name="01907801500004" ll="SDBH:צוּר:000001">磐石</a>​<a name="01907801500002" ll="SDBH:בקע:000001">裂开</a>​，​多多​地​<a name="01907801500014" ll="SDBH:שׁקה:000002">给</a>​他们​<a name="01907801500014" ll="SDBH:שׁקה:000002">水</a>​<a name="01907801500014" ll="SDBH:שׁקה:000002">喝</a>​，​如​从​<a name="01907801500018;01907801500020" ll="SDBH:רַב:000002;SDBH:תְּהֹום:000000">深渊</a>​而​出​。
    
\v 16 他​使​<a name="01907801600006" ll="SDBH:נזל:000001">水</a>​从​<a name="01907801600010" ll="SDBH:סֶלַע:000000">磐石</a>​<a name="01907801600004" ll="SDBH:יצא:000023">涌出</a>​，​叫​<a name="01907801600022" ll="SDBH:מַיִם:000000" il="Water_drop_001">水</a>​如​<a name="01907801600020" ll="SDBH:נָהָר:000000">江河</a>​<a name="01907801600014" ll="SDBH:ירד:000008">下流</a>​。
    
\v 17 他们​却​<a name="01907801700004;01907801700006">仍旧</a>​<a name="01907801700010" ll="SDBH:חטא:001005">得罪</a>​他​，​在​<a name="01907801700024" ll="SDBH:צִיָּה:000001">干旱</a>​<a name="01907801700024" ll="SDBH:צִיָּה:000001">之</a>​<a name="01907801700024" ll="SDBH:צִיָּה:000001">地</a>​<a name="01907801700016" ll="SDBH:מרה:000000">悖逆</a>​<a name="01907801700018" ll="SDBH:עֶלְיֹון:000000">至高者</a>​。
    
\v 18 他们​<a name="01907801800010" ll="SDBH:לֵבָב:000001">心</a>​中​<a name="01907801800004" ll="SDBH:נסה:000000">试探</a>​<a name="01907801800006" ll="SDBH:אֵל:000001">上帝</a>​，​随​自己​<a name="01907801800020" ll="SDBH:נֶפֶשׁ:000001">所</a>​<a name="01907801800020" ll="SDBH:נֶפֶשׁ:000001">欲</a>​<a name="01907801800020" ll="SDBH:נֶפֶשׁ:000001">的</a>​<a name="01907801800014" ll="SDBH:שׁאל:000000">求</a>​<a name="01907801800016" ll="SDBH:אֹכֶל:000000">食物</a>​，
    
\v 19 并且​<a name="01907801900004" ll="SDBH:דבר:001000">妄论</a>​<a name="01907801900008" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000002">上帝</a>​<a name="01907801900010" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">说</a>​：​​“<a name="01907801900016" ll="SDBH:אֵל:000001">上帝</a>​岂​<a name="01907801900014" ll="SDBH:יכל:000000">能</a>​在​<a name="01907801900028" ll="SDBH:מִדְבָּר:000000" il="RS26447_ISR91T-418;Sinai-191;Sinai-220;Sinai-3;Sinai178;Sinai190;tb113006604">旷野</a>​<a name="01907801900020" ll="SDBH:ערך:000001">摆设</a>​<a name="01907801900022" ll="SDBH:שֻׁלְחָן:000000" il="Realia:5.7b">筵席</a>​吗​？
    
\v 20 他​虽​曾​<a name="01907802000004">击打</a>​<a name="01907802000006" ll="SDBH:צוּר:000001">磐石</a>​，​使​<a name="01907802000012" ll="SDBH:מַיִם:000000" il="Water_drop_001">水</a>​<a name="01907802000010" ll="SDBH:זוב:000000">涌出</a>​，​如​<a name="01907802000016" ll="SDBH:נַחַל:000000" il="NBGbs20090428-1_39;tb110603119">江河</a>​<a name="01907802000018" ll="SDBH:שׁטף:000001">泛滥</a>​；​他​还​<a name="01907802000026" ll="SDBH:יכל:000000">能</a>​<a name="01907802000028">赐</a>​<a name="01907802000024" ll="SDBH:לֶחֶם:000000" il="Tandır_bread;tb061116157">粮食</a>​吗​？​还​能​为​他​的​<a name="01907802000038" ll="SDBH:עַם:000000">百姓</a>​<a name="01907802000032" ll="SDBH:כון:000019">预备</a>​吃​的​<a name="01907802000034" ll="SDBH:שְׁאֵר:000002">肉</a>​吗​？​”
    
\v 21 <a name="01907802100002">所以</a>​，​<a name="01907802100006">耶和华</a>​<a name="01907802100004">听见</a>​就​<a name="01907802100010" ll="SDBH:עבר:001000">发怒</a>​，​有​<a name="01907802100014" ll="SDBH:אֵשׁ:000000">烈火</a>​向​<a name="01907802100020" ll="SDBH:יַעֲקֹב:000000">雅各</a>​<a name="01907802100016" ll="SDBH:נשׂק:000001">点燃</a>​，​有​<a name="01907802100026" ll="SDBH:אַף:000008">怒气</a>​向​<a name="01907802100032" ll="SDBH:יִשְׂרָאֵל:000000">以色列</a>​<a name="01907802100028" ll="SDBH:עלה:000022">上腾</a>​；
    
\v 22 因为​他们​不​<a name="01907802200006" ll="SDBH:אמן:000005">信服</a>​<a name="01907802200010" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000002">上帝</a>​，​不​<a name="01907802200016" ll="SDBH:בטח:000001">倚赖</a>​他​的​<a name="01907802200020" ll="SDBH:יְשׁוּעָה:000000">拯救</a>​。
    
\v 23 然而​他​却​<a name="01907802300004" ll="SDBH:צוה:000000">吩咐</a>​<a name="01907802300006" ll="SDBH:שַׁחַק:000002">天空</a>​，​又​<a name="01907802300018" ll="SDBH:פתח:000001">敞开</a>​<a name="01907802300016" ll="SDBH:שָׁמַיִם:000000">天</a>​<a name="01907802300016" ll="SDBH:שָׁמַיִם:000000">上</a>​的​<a name="01907802300014" ll="SDBH:דֶּלֶת:000003">门</a>​，
    
\v 24 <a name="01907802400004" ll="SDBH:מטר:000000" il="Rain;Rain2">降</a>​<a name="01907802400008" ll="SDBH:מָן:000000">吗哪</a>​像​雨​，​给​他们​<a name="01907802400012" ll="SDBH:אכל:000000">吃</a>​，​将​<a name="01907802400018" ll="SDBH:שָׁמַיִם:000000">天</a>​<a name="01907802400018" ll="SDBH:שָׁמַיִם:000000">上</a>​的​<a name="01907802400016" ll="SDBH:דָּגָן:000000" il="Flora:3.1">粮食</a>​<a name="01907802400020">赐给</a>​他们​。
    
\v 25 <a name="01907802500008">各人</a>​就​<a name="01907802500006" ll="SDBH:אכל:000000">吃</a>​<a name="01907802500004" ll="SDBH:אַבִּיר:000006">大能者</a>​的​<a name="01907802500002" ll="SDBH:לֶחֶם:000000" il="Tandır_bread;tb061116157">食物</a>​；​他​<a name="01907802500012" ll="SDBH:שׁלח:000006">赐下</a>​<a name="01907802500010" ll="SDBH:צֵידָה:000000">粮食</a>​，​使​他们​<a name="01907802500018" ll="SDBH:שֹׂבַע:000000">饱足</a>​。
    
\v 26 他​令​<a name="01907802600004" ll="SDBH:קָדִים:000002" il="Gale_Force_Winds">东风</a>​<a name="01907802600002" ll="SDBH:נסע:000004">吹</a>​在​<a name="01907802600010" ll="SDBH:שָׁמַיִם:000000">天空</a>​，​用​<a name="01907802600018" ll="SDBH:עֹז:000002">能力</a>​<a name="01907802600014">引来</a>​<a name="01907802600020" ll="SDBH:תֵּימָן:000001">南风</a>​。
    
\v 27 他​<a name="01907802700004" ll="SDBH:מטר:000000" il="Rain;Rain2">降</a>​<a name="01907802700014" ll="SDBH:שְׁאֵר:000002">肉</a>​像​雨​，​多​如​<a name="01907802700012" ll="SDBH:עָפָר:000000">尘土</a>​，​降​<a name="01907802700024;01907802700026" ll="SDBH:כָּנָף:000000;SDBH:עֹוף:000000" il="HK00072;HK00081;HK00084;LB00071;PikiWiki_Israel_16912">飞鸟</a>​，​多​如​<a name="01907802700020;01907802700022" ll="SDBH:חֹול:000000;SDBH:יָם:000000" il="Rough_seas;Sand">海沙</a>​，
    
\v 28 <a name="01907802800004" ll="SDBH:נפל:000001" tl="HOTTP2413">落</a>​在​他​自己​的​<a name="01907802800010" ll="SDBH:מַחֲנֶה:000000" il="HK00220;HK00221;HK00223;il_israel_camp_sinai;il_jordan_crossing_d01">营</a>​<a name="01907802800008">中</a>​，​在​他​<a name="01907802800016" ll="SDBH:מִשְׁכָּן:000001">帐幕</a>​的​<a name="01907802800012" ll="SDBH:סָבִיב:000000">四周围</a>​。
    
\v 29 他们​<a name="01907802900004" ll="SDBH:אכל:000000">吃</a>​了​，​而且​<a name="01907802900008" ll="SDBH:שׂבע:000000">饱足</a>​；​这样​就​随​了​他们​<a name="01907802900014" ll="SDBH:תַּאֲוָה:000000">所</a>​<a name="01907802900014" ll="SDBH:תַּאֲוָה:000000">欲</a>​<a name="01907802900014" ll="SDBH:תַּאֲוָה:000000">的</a>​。
    
\v 30 但​在​他们​满足​<a name="01907803000008" ll="SDBH:תַּאֲוָה:000000">食欲</a>​以前​，​<a name="01907803000012" ll="SDBH:אֹכֶל:000000">食物</a>​<a name="01907803000010">还</a>​在​他们​<a name="01907803000016" ll="SDBH:פֶּה:000000">口</a>​中​的​时候​，
    
\v 31 <a name="01907803100006" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000002">上帝</a>​的​<a name="01907803100004" ll="SDBH:אַף:000008">怒气</a>​就​向​他们​<a name="01907803100008" ll="SDBH:עלה:000022">上腾</a>​，​<a name="01907803100014" ll="SDBH:הרג:000000">杀</a>​了​他们​当中​<a name="01907803100018" ll="SDBH:מִשְׁמָן:000002">肥壮</a>​<a name="01907803100018" ll="SDBH:מִשְׁמָן:000002">的</a>​<a name="01907803100018" ll="SDBH:מִשְׁמָן:000002">人</a>​，​<a name="01907803100026" ll="SDBH:כרע:000001">打倒</a>​<a name="01907803100024" ll="SDBH:יִשְׂרָאֵל:000000">以色列</a>​的​<a name="01907803100022" ll="SDBH:בָּחוּר:000000">青年</a>​。
    
\v 32 <a name="01907803200004">虽</a>​<a name="01907803200004">是</a>​<a name="01907803200004">这样</a>​，​他们​<a name="01907803200010">仍旧</a>​<a name="01907803200008" ll="SDBH:חטא:001005">犯罪</a>​，​不​<a name="01907803200016" ll="SDBH:אמן:000005">信</a>​他​<a name="01907803200020" ll="SDBH:פלא:000000">奇妙</a>​<a name="01907803200020" ll="SDBH:פלא:000000">的</a>​<a name="01907803200020" ll="SDBH:פלא:000000">作为</a>​。
    
\v 33 因此​，​他​使​他们​的​<a name="01907803300012" ll="SDBH:יֹום:000004">日子</a>​全​归​<a name="01907803300010" ll="SDBH:הֶבֶל:000002">虚空</a>​，​叫​他们​的​<a name="01907803300016" ll="SDBH:שָׁנָה:000000">年岁</a>​尽​属​<a name="01907803300022" ll="SDBH:בֶּהָלָה:000000">惊恐</a>​。
    
\v 34 他​<a name="01907803400004" ll="SDBH:הרג:000000">杀</a>​他们​的​时候​，​他们​才​<a name="01907803400008" ll="SDBH:דרשׁ:000003">求问</a>​他​，​<a name="01907803400012" ll="SDBH:שׁוב:000041">回心转意</a>​，​<a name="01907803400016" ll="SDBH:שׁחר:001001">切切</a>​<a name="01907803400016" ll="SDBH:שׁחר:001001">寻求</a>​<a name="01907803400018" ll="SDBH:אֵל:000001" tl="HOTTP2414">上帝</a>​。
    
\v 35 他们​<a name="01907803500004" ll="SDBH:זכר:000000">追念</a>​<a name="01907803500008" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000002">上帝</a>​是​他们​的​<a name="01907803500010" ll="SDBH:צוּר:000002">磐石</a>​，​<a name="01907803500016" ll="SDBH:עֶלְיֹון:000000">至高</a>​的​<a name="01907803500014" ll="SDBH:אֵל:000003">上帝</a>​是​他们​的​<a name="01907803500018" ll="SDBH:גאל:000003">救赎主</a>​。
    
\v 36 他们​却​用​<a name="01907803600008" ll="SDBH:פֶּה:000000">口</a>​<a name="01907803600004" ll="SDBH:פתה:000001">谄媚</a>​他​，​用​<a name="01907803600014" ll="SDBH:לָשֹׁון:000000">舌</a>​向​他​<a name="01907803600016" ll="SDBH:כזב:000000">说谎</a>​。
    
\v 37 他们​的​<a name="01907803700004" ll="SDBH:לֵב:000001">心</a>​向​他​不​<a name="01907803700008" ll="SDBH:כון:000007">坚定</a>​，​不​<a name="01907803700016" ll="SDBH:אמן:000006">忠于</a>​他​的​<a name="01907803700020" ll="SDBH:בְּרִית:000000">约</a>​。
    
\v 38 但​他​有​<a name="01907803800006" ll="SDBH:רַחוּם:000000">怜悯</a>​，​<a name="01907803800008" ll="SDBH:כפר:000005">赦免</a>​他们​的​<a name="01907803800010" ll="SDBH:עָוֹן:000000">罪孽</a>​，​没有​<a name="01907803800016" ll="SDBH:שׁחת:000001">灭绝</a>​他们​，​而且​<a name="01907803800020">屡次</a>​<a name="01907803800024" ll="SDBH:שׁוב:000020">撤销</a>​他​的​<a name="01907803800026" ll="SDBH:אַף:000008">怒气</a>​，​不​<a name="01907803800032;01907803800034" ll="SDBH:עור:000004">发尽</a>​他​的​<a name="01907803800036" ll="SDBH:חֵמָה:001001">愤怒</a>​。
    
\v 39 他​<a name="01907803900004" ll="SDBH:זכר:000000">想念</a>​他们​不过​是​<a name="01907803900008" ll="SDBH:בָּשָׂר:000004">血肉</a>​<a name="01907803900008" ll="SDBH:בָּשָׂר:000004">之</a>​<a name="01907803900008" ll="SDBH:בָּשָׂר:000004">躯</a>​，​是​一​阵​<a name="01907803900014" ll="SDBH:הלך:000000">去</a>​而​不​<a name="01907803900020" ll="SDBH:שׁוב:000022">返</a>​的​<a name="01907803900012" ll="SDBH:רוּחַ:000004" il="Gale_Force_Winds">风</a>​。
    
\v 40 他们​在​<a name="01907804000012" ll="SDBH:מִדְבָּר:000000" il="RS26447_ISR91T-418;Sinai-191;Sinai-220;Sinai-3;Sinai178;Sinai190;tb113006604">旷野</a>​<a name="01907804000006" ll="SDBH:מרה:000000">悖逆</a>​他​，​在​<a name="01907804000018" ll="SDBH:יְשִׁימֹון:000000">荒地</a>​令​他​<a name="01907804000014" ll="SDBH:עצב:000001">担忧</a>​，​何其​多​呢​！
    
\v 41 他们​<a name="01907804100004" ll="SDBH:שׁוב:000041">再三</a>​<a name="01907804100008" ll="SDBH:נסה:000000">试探</a>​<a name="01907804100010" ll="SDBH:אֵל:000001">上帝</a>​，​<a name="01907804100018" ll="SDBH:תוה:001000">惹动</a>​<a name="01907804100016" ll="SDBH:יִשְׂרָאֵל:000000">以色列</a>​的​<a name="01907804100014" ll="SDBH:קָדֹושׁ:000000">圣者</a>​。
    
\v 42 他们​不​<a name="01907804200004" ll="SDBH:זכר:000000">追念</a>​他​<a name="01907804200008">手</a>​的​能力​，​和​他​<a name="01907804200014" ll="SDBH:פדה:000002">救赎</a>​他们​脱离​<a name="01907804200018" ll="SDBH:צַר:000003">敌人</a>​的​<a name="01907804200010" ll="SDBH:יֹום:000003">日子</a>​；
    
\v 43 他​怎样​在​<a name="01907804300008" ll="SDBH:מִצְרַיִם:000001" il="Egyptian_temple;Gizah_Pyramids;Goshen;NBGbs20120205-81;NBGbs20120205-82;NBGbs20120207-20;NBGbs20140204-40;tb010705951">埃及</a>​<a name="01907804300004" ll="SDBH:שׂים:000013">显</a>​<a name="01907804300010" ll="SDBH:אֹות:000002">神迹</a>​，​在​<a name="01907804300020" ll="SDBH:צֹעַן:000000">琐安</a>​<a name="01907804300018" ll="SDBH:שָׂדֶה:000001">田</a>​显​<a name="01907804300014" ll="SDBH:מֹופֵת:000001">奇事</a>​，
    
\v 44 把​<a name="01907804400010" ll="SDBH:יְאֹר:000002">江河</a>​并​<a name="01907804400014" ll="SDBH:נזל:000001">河汊</a>​的​水​都​<a name="01907804400004" ll="SDBH:הפך:000009">变为</a>​<a name="01907804400008" ll="SDBH:דָּם:000000" il="Blood">血</a>​，​使​他们​<a name="01907804400016" ll="SDBH:בַּל:000000">不</a>​能​<a name="01907804400018" ll="SDBH:שׁתה:000000">喝</a>​。
    
\v 45 他​使​<a name="01907804500006" ll="SDBH:עָרֹב:000000" il="Fauna:6.4">苍蝇</a>​<a name="01907804500006" ll="SDBH:עָרֹב:000000" il="Fauna:6.4">成群</a>​<a name="01907804500002" ll="SDBH:שׁלח:000002">落</a>​在​他们​当中​，​<a name="01907804500010" ll="SDBH:אכל:000002">吃尽</a>​他们​，​又​叫​<a name="01907804500014" ll="SDBH:צְפַרְדֵּעַ:000000" il="BK00023;Fauna:5.2a">青蛙</a>​<a name="01907804500018" ll="SDBH:שׁחת:000001">灭</a>​了​他们​，
    
\v 46 将​他们​的​<a name="01907804600012" ll="SDBH:יְבוּל:000000">果实</a>​<a name="01907804600004">交给</a>​<a name="01907804600010" ll="SDBH:חָסִיל:000000" il="Fauna:6.9a;Fauna:6.9b;Fauna:6.9d;Fauna:6.9e">蚂蚱</a>​，​把​他们​<a name="01907804600016" ll="SDBH:יְגִיעַ:000000">劳碌</a>​<a name="01907804600016" ll="SDBH:יְגִיעַ:000000">得来</a>​<a name="01907804600016" ll="SDBH:יְגִיעַ:000000">的</a>​交给​<a name="01907804600022" ll="SDBH:אַרְבֶּה:000000" il="Fauna:6.9a;Fauna:6.9b;Fauna:6.9d;Fauna:6.9e;Locusta_migratoria_(gregarious_phase)_(5012171245)">蝗虫</a>​。
    
\v 47 他​降​<a name="01907804700008" ll="SDBH:בָּרָד:000000" il="Hail_on_ground">冰雹</a>​<a name="01907804700002" ll="SDBH:הרג:000000">打坏</a>​他们​的​<a name="01907804700010" ll="SDBH:גֶּפֶן:000001" il="Flora:2.12a;Flora:2.12b;HK00112;LB00107;tb061504248;tb111706130;vineyard1679, rp">葡萄树</a>​，​下​<a name="01907804700020" ll="SDBH:חֲנָמַל:000000" il="frost">寒霜</a>​打坏​他们​的​<a name="01907804700014" ll="SDBH:שִׁקְמָה:000000" il="Flora:2.11a;Flora:2.11c;Flora:2.6c">桑树</a>​，
    
\v 48 将​他们​的​<a name="01907804800012" ll="SDBH:בְּעִיר:000000" il="NBGbs20120208-08">牲畜</a>​<a name="01907804800004" ll="SDBH:סגר:000004">交给</a>​<a name="01907804800010" ll="SDBH:בָּרָד:000000" il="Hail_on_ground" tl="HOTTP2415">冰雹</a>​，​把​他们​的​<a name="01907804800016" ll="SDBH:מִקְנֶה:000001" il="NBGbs20120208-08">群畜</a>​交给​<a name="01907804800022" ll="SDBH:רֶשֶׁף:000000">闪电</a>​。
    
\v 49 他​<a name="01907804900002" ll="SDBH:שׁלח:000020">使</a>​<a name="01907804900006" ll="SDBH:חָרֹון:000001">猛烈</a>​<a name="01907804900006" ll="SDBH:חָרֹון:000001">的</a>​<a name="01907804900008" ll="SDBH:אַף:000008">怒气</a>​和​<a name="01907804900010" ll="SDBH:עֶבְרָה:000001">愤怒</a>​、​<a name="01907804900014" ll="SDBH:זַעַם:000000">恼恨</a>​、​<a name="01907804900018" ll="SDBH:צָרָה:000000">苦难</a>​，​成​了​<a name="01907804900020" ll="SDBH:מִשְׁלַחַת:000001">一</a>​<a name="01907804900020" ll="SDBH:מִשְׁלַחַת:000001">群</a>​降​<a name="01907804900024" ll="SDBH:רַע:000004">灾</a>​的​<a name="01907804900022" ll="SDBH:מַלְאָךְ:000000">使者</a>​，​<a name="01907804900002" ll="SDBH:שׁלח:000020">临到</a>​他们​。
    
\v 50 他​为​自己​的​<a name="01907805000008" ll="SDBH:אַף:000008">怒气</a>​<a name="01907805000002" ll="SDBH:פלס:000000">修平</a>​了​<a name="01907805000004" ll="SDBH:נָתִיב:000000">路</a>​，​将​他们​的​<a name="01907805000022" ll="SDBH:חַיָּה:000002">性命</a>​<a name="01907805000030" ll="SDBH:סגר:000004">交给</a>​<a name="01907805000028" ll="SDBH:דֶּבֶר:000000">瘟疫</a>​，​使​<a name="01907805000018" ll="SDBH:נֶפֶשׁ:000001">他们</a>​<a name="01907805000016" ll="SDBH:מָוֶת:000000">死亡</a>​，
    
\v 51 在​<a name="01907805100012" ll="SDBH:מִצְרַיִם:000001" il="Egyptian_temple;Gizah_Pyramids;Goshen;NBGbs20120205-81;NBGbs20120205-82;NBGbs20120207-20;NBGbs20140204-40;tb010705951">埃及</a>​<a name="01907805100004">击杀</a>​<a name="01907805100006">所有</a>​<a name="01907805100006">的</a>​<a name="01907805100008" ll="SDBH:בְּכֹור:000000">长子</a>​，​在​<a name="01907805100022" ll="SDBH:חָם:002001">含</a>​的​<a name="01907805100020" ll="SDBH:אֹהֶל:000003">帐棚</a>​中​击杀​他们​<a name="01907805100016" ll="SDBH:אֹון:000000">壮年</a>​<a name="01907805100016" ll="SDBH:אֹון:000000">时</a>​<a name="01907805100014" ll="SDBH:רֵאשִׁית:000005">头生</a>​<a name="01907805100014" ll="SDBH:רֵאשִׁית:000005">的</a>​。
    
\v 52 他​却​<a name="01907805200004" ll="SDBH:נסע:000002">领出</a>​自己​的​<a name="01907805200012" ll="SDBH:עַם:000000">子民</a>​如​<a name="01907805200010" ll="SDBH:צֹאן:000000" il="LB00012;LB00015;LB00017;NBGbs20120208-08;NBGbs20120710-139;NBGpb20140401b;Realia:1.2.1;tb111706002">羊</a>​，​在​<a name="01907805200028" ll="SDBH:מִדְבָּר:000000" il="RS26447_ISR91T-418;Sinai-191;Sinai-220;Sinai-3;Sinai178;Sinai190;tb113006604">旷野</a>​<a name="01907805200016">引导</a>​他们​如​<a name="01907805200022" ll="SDBH:עֵדֶר:000000" il="LB00012;LB00015;LB00017;NBGbs20120208-08;NBGbs20120710-139;NBGpb20140401b;Realia:1.2.1;tb111706002">羊群</a>​。
    
\v 53 他​<a name="01907805300004" ll="SDBH:נחה:000000">领</a>​他们​<a name="01907805300008" ll="SDBH:בֶּטַח:000000">稳稳妥妥</a>​<a name="01907805300008" ll="SDBH:בֶּטַח:000000">地</a>​，​使​他们​不致​<a name="01907805300014" ll="SDBH:פחד:000000">害怕</a>​；​<a name="01907805300026" ll="SDBH:יָם:000000" il="Rough_seas">海</a>​却​<a name="01907805300022" ll="SDBH:כסה:000000">淹没</a>​他们​的​<a name="01907805300020" ll="SDBH:איב:000001">仇敌</a>​。
    
\v 54 他​<a name="01907805400004">带</a>​他们​到​自己​<a name="01907805400010" ll="SDBH:קֹדֶשׁ:000001">圣地</a>​的​<a name="01907805400008" ll="SDBH:גְּבוּל:000000">边界</a>​，​到​他​<a name="01907805400018" ll="SDBH:יָמִין:000000">右手</a>​所​<a name="01907805400016" ll="SDBH:קנה:000000">得</a>​的​这​<a name="01907805400012" ll="SDBH:הַר:000000">山地</a>​。
    
\v 55 他​在​他们​<a name="01907805500008">面前</a>​<a name="01907805500004" ll="SDBH:גרשׁ:000002">赶出</a>​<a name="01907805500010" ll="SDBH:גֹּוי:000000">外邦人</a>​，​用​<a name="01907805500018" ll="SDBH:חֶבֶל:000000" il="Realia:1.14">绳子</a>​<a name="01907805500014" ll="SDBH:נפל:000032">抽签</a>​量​地​给​他们​为​<a name="01907805500020" ll="SDBH:נַחֲלָה:000000">业</a>​，​让​<a name="01907805500032" ll="SDBH:יִשְׂרָאֵל:000000">以色列</a>​<a name="01907805500030" ll="SDBH:שֵׁבֶט:000006">支派</a>​的​人​<a name="01907805500024" ll="SDBH:שׁכן:000001">住</a>​在​自己​的​<a name="01907805500028" ll="SDBH:אֹהֶל:000003">帐棚</a>​里​。
    
\v 56 他们​仍旧​<a name="01907805600004" ll="SDBH:נסה:000000">试探</a>​，​<a name="01907805600008" ll="SDBH:מרה:000000">悖逆</a>​<a name="01907805600014" ll="SDBH:עֶלְיֹון:000000">至高</a>​的​<a name="01907805600012" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000002">上帝</a>​，​不​<a name="01907805600022" ll="SDBH:שׁמר:000003">遵守</a>​他​的​<a name="01907805600018" ll="SDBH:עֵדָה:002000;SDBH:עֵדוּת:000000">法度</a>​，
    
\v 57 反倒​<a name="01907805700004" ll="SDBH:סוג:000002">退后</a>​，​<a name="01907805700008" ll="SDBH:בגד:000000">行</a>​<a name="01907805700008" ll="SDBH:בגד:000000">诡诈</a>​，​像​他们​的​<a name="01907805700012" ll="SDBH:אָב:000001">祖宗</a>​一样​，​他们​<a name="01907805700014" ll="SDBH:הפך:000008">翻转</a>​，​如同​<a name="01907805700020" ll="SDBH:רְמִיָּה:000001">松弛</a>​的​<a name="01907805700018" ll="SDBH:קֶשֶׁת:000000" il="Realia:2.14.1a;Realia:2.14.1b">弓</a>​，
    
\v 58 以​<a name="01907805800008" ll="SDBH:בָּמָה:000002" il="Flora:1.18.1a;adr0807089001;ws040616035">丘坛</a>​<a name="01907805800004" ll="SDBH:כעס:000001">惹</a>​他​<a name="01907805800004" ll="SDBH:כעס:000001">发怒</a>​，​以​<a name="01907805800014" ll="SDBH:פָּסִיל:000000" il="Realia:4.6b;adr1305227007">雕刻</a>​<a name="01907805800014" ll="SDBH:פָּסִיל:000000" il="Realia:4.6b;adr1305227007">的</a>​<a name="01907805800014" ll="SDBH:פָּסִיל:000000" il="Realia:4.6b;adr1305227007">偶像</a>​使​他​<a name="01907805800016" ll="SDBH:קנא:000002">忌恨</a>​。
    
\v 59 <a name="01907805900004" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000002">上帝</a>​<a name="01907805900002">听见</a>​就​<a name="01907805900008" ll="SDBH:עבר:001000">发怒</a>​，​<a name="01907805900014" ll="SDBH:מְאֹד:000001">全然</a>​<a name="01907805900012" ll="SDBH:מאס:000000">弃绝</a>​了​<a name="01907805900018" ll="SDBH:יִשְׂרָאֵל:000000">以色列</a>​，
    
