\v 70 他​<a name="01907807000004" ll="SDBH:בחר:000000">拣选</a>​他​的​<a name="01907807000010" ll="SDBH:עֶבֶד:000000" il="Bolen00049">仆人</a>​<a name="01907807000008" ll="SDBH:דָּוִד:000000" il="tb061616894">大卫</a>​，​从​<a name="01907807000018;01907807000020" ll="SDBH:מִכְלָא:000000;SDBH:צֹאן:000000" il="LB00012;LB00015;LB00017;NBGbs20120208-08;NBGbs20120710-139;NBGpb20140401b;Realia:1.2.1;tb111706002">羊圈</a>​中​将​他​<a name="01907807000014" ll="SDBH:לקח:000000">召来</a>​，
    
\v 71 叫​他​不再​牧放​那些​母羊​，​为​要​<a name="01907807100012" ll="SDBH:רעה:000001" il="BK00005;BK00010;HK00009;LB00001;LB00013;NBGpb20140401b;Realia:1.2.1;Shepherd">牧养</a>​自己​的​<a name="01907807100018" ll="SDBH:עַם:000000">百姓</a>​<a name="01907807100016" ll="SDBH:יַעֲקֹב:000000">雅各</a>和​自己​的​<a name="01907807100026" ll="SDBH:נַחֲלָה:000000" tl="HOTTP2416">产业</a>​<a name="01907807100024" ll="SDBH:יִשְׂרָאֵל:000000" tl="HOTTP2416">以色列</a>​。
    
\v 72 于是​，​他​以​<a name="01907807200008" ll="SDBH:תֹּם:000001">纯正</a>​<a name="01907807200008" ll="SDBH:תֹּם:000001">的</a>​<a name="01907807200010" ll="SDBH:לֵבָב:000001">心</a>​<a name="01907807200004" ll="SDBH:רעה:000001" il="BK00005;BK00010;HK00009;LB00001;LB00013;NBGpb20140401b;Realia:1.2.1;Shepherd">牧养</a>​他们​，​用​<a name="01907807200016" ll="SDBH:תְּבוּנָה:000000">巧妙</a>​<a name="01907807200016" ll="SDBH:תְּבוּנָה:000000">的</a>​<a name="01907807200018" ll="SDBH:כַּף:000001">手</a>​<a name="01907807200020" ll="SDBH:נחה:000000">引导</a>​他们​。
