    <a name="01911400300014" ll="SDBH:יַרְדֵּן:000000" il="Jordan_River_in_area_of_Jordan_River_park;RS26381_ISR91T-1831;RS26385_ISR91T-187">约旦</a>​<a name="01911400300014" ll="SDBH:יַרְדֵּן:000000" il="Jordan_River_in_area_of_Jordan_River_park;RS26381_ISR91T-1831;RS26385_ISR91T-187">河</a>​也​<a name="01911400300016;01911400300020" ll="SDBH:אָחֹור:000001">倒流</a>​。
    
